about-a: This interactive map was developed by the community.
about-b: Click the Features tab above to filter the map to display Oculi, ores, plants, monsters, and more.
about-c: Double-click a feature marker to flag it as done. For some features such as chests, a single click will display a popup with more information, including an image or comment.
about-d: Click the Routes tab above to filter the map to display community made farming routes, such as ones to efficiently collect regional specialties or fight monsters.
